cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.HC 

This paper deals with inverse reinforcement learning, a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) that involves modeling human behavior (cs.HC) and developing algorithms for decision-making (cs.LG) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of summarizing functions, which are relevant to systems and control (cs.SY).
